title: Vote4me
info:
Ranked 6th in the 4 channel music compo at Assembly 1994.

Lyrics:

Yo, yo! Let's go!

This is Leinad of Avalanche fame
I'm out of money and know what to blame
But I got an idea.. why don't you vote4me?
In the music competition and then we'll see

I will be so happy with the tiny little prize
Of course, I will mind some cash
But if you vote4me and I'll be among the free
Chances off that you will leave to see tomorrow(?)
